show.description: 10-crore ka cheque leke business tycoon Vibhu jab sanyasi banne Mahaguru Dayanand ke aashram me ghusta hai, tab poore aashram me hungama mach jaata hai.  Par paap ki is duniya me entry ki keemat sirf paisa hai, ya Guruji ke sabse kareeb pahunchne ke liye Vibhu ko apni jaan-izzat tak daav par lagani padegi?
